latestIgtvVideos.title: MY DISABILITY STORY
latestIgtvVideos.caption:
Posting this video today on this DISABILITY PRIDE MONTH -July ✨. Here I've shared about my disability, the problems I've faced, how I Overcame and SELF LOVE ♥️.

Lets listen to disabled people about their life experiences, stories, problems and let's support them, respect them, honour them and give them more chances in the industry. They deserve it 🔥💪.

we all are different. we all are unique. we all are beautiful 🌈🦋

Watch this video without skipping & If you like the video then do share it with your friends and family Circle and spread the awareness thank you🙏🌼
